:: Leave the General Shop
You step back out into the busy market street.

[[Market Street]]

:: Suspicious Man
A tall, cloaked figure leans against a merchant's stall. His face is hidden in shadow. He watches the crowd with the intensity of a hawk.

As you approach, he turns his gaze toward you.

"You're new," he says, his voice like gravel. "I don't recognize you from the town."

(if: not $suspiciousManMet)[
  (set: $suspiciousManMet to true)
  (set: $reputation to $reputation + 1)
]

[[Ask who he is]]
[[Ask about the forest]]
[[Walk away]]

:: Ask who he is
"I am called **Silas**," he replies coolly. "I work in... acquisition. I find things that are lost. I trade in goods that are hard to come by."

He eyes you carefully. "You seem like someone who might be useful. Interested in making some extra gold?"

[[Ask what he wants]]
[[Accept his proposition]]
[[Walk away]]

:: Ask about the forest
Silas's expression hardens. "The forest is not a topic I discuss lightly. But I'll tell you this—there's something valuable in there. Something that could change everything."

He pulls out a small, intricately carved box. "If you can retrieve what's hidden in the forest, I'll pay handsomely."

[[Ask what he wants]]
[[Accept his proposition]]
[[Walk away]]

:: Ask what he wants
"I want you to find something for me," Silas explains. "In the forest, there's an artifact. An ancient stone with strange markings. Bring it to me, and you'll be rewarded."

He looks at you intensely. "100 gold. Do we have a deal?"

[[Accept his proposition]]
[[Decline politely]]
[[Walk away]]

:: Accept his proposition
(if: not $silasQuestAccepted)[
  (set: $silasQuestAccepted to true)
  "Excellent," Silas says with a thin smile. "Bring me the ancient stone. I'll be waiting."
  (unless: "Find the artifact for Silas (Reward: 100 gold)" is in $questLog)[
    (set: $questLog to $questLog + (a: "Find the artifact for Silas (Reward: 100 gold)"))
  ]
  (set: $reputation to $reputation + 1)
]
(else)[
  Silas nods. "Good to see you again. Any luck finding that artifact?"
]

[[Ask about the forest]]
[[Walk away]]

:: Decline politely
"Your loss," Silas shrugs, turning back to the crowd.

[[Walk away]]

:: Walk away
You step away from Silas, unsettled but intrigued.

[[Market Street]]

:: Food Stall
A cheerful vendor tends to a small stall laden with fresh pastries, roasted vegetables, and hot soup.

"Fresh food, friend!" she calls out. "Warm your belly and sharpen your mind!"

[[Buy Hearty Soup (8 gp)]] — Restores 20 health
[[Buy Roasted Vegetables (6 gp)]] — Restores 10 health
[[Buy Pastry (4 gp)]] — Restores 5 health
[[Return to Market Street]]

:: Buy Hearty Soup (8 gp)
(if: $gold >= 8)[
  (set: $gold to $gold - 8)
  (set: $health to (min: 100, $health + 20))
  "Enjoy, friend!"
]
(else)[
  "You don't have enough gold."
]

[[Buy Roasted Vegetables (6 gp)]]
[[Buy Pastry (4 gp)]]
[[Return to Market Street]]

